<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no" />
  <title>7LM | Connect Comercial</title>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@500;700&family=Outfit:wght@400;600;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../02_recursos/01_estilos/inicio.css?v=20260406-litefx1" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../02_recursos/01_estilos/operacoes.css?v=20260406-litefx1" />
  <script src="/02_recursos/02_scripts/preload_portal.js?v=20260407-theme-persist1"></script>
  <script src="/02_recursos/02_scripts/ui_text_normalizer.js?v=20260401-textfix2" defer></script>
</head>
<body class="tl-home tl-ops-page tl-ops-redesign">
  <div class="tl-atmos-layer">
    <div class="tl-blob tl-blob--teal"></div>
    <div class="tl-blob tl-blob--purple"></div>
    <div id="tl-particles-container"></div>
    <div class="tl-glass-overlay"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="tl-shell">
    <aside class="tl-sidebar glass-panel hyper-glass" id="sidebar"></aside>

    <main class="tl-main">
      <header class="tl-topbar tl-ops-topbar anim-stagger-1">
        <div class="tl-topbar__titles">
          <div class="tl-overline reveal-text">MODULO COMERCIAL 7LM</div>
          <h1 class="tl-title reveal-text delay-1">Connect Comercial</h1>
          <p class="tl-subtitle reveal-text delay-2">
            O antigo Connect Plataforma foi consolidado com o Connect Imoveis em um unico modulo.
            A frente comercial agora segue a sequencia Clientes, Simulador e Imoveis.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="tl-topbar__controls">
          <button id="btnTema" class="tl-btn-icon glass-panel hyper-glass" aria-label="Alternar tema">
            <div class="icon-wrap">
              <svg class="icon-sun" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"></circle>
                <line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="3"></line>
                <line x1="12" y1="21" x2="12" y2="23"></line>
                <line x1="4.22" y1="4.22" x2="5.64" y2="5.64"></line>
                <line x1="18.36" y1="18.36" x2="19.78" y2="19.78"></line>
                <line x1="1" y1="12" x2="3" y2="12"></line>
                <line x1="21" y1="12" x2="23" y2="12"></line>
                <line x1="4.22" y1="19.78" x2="5.64" y2="18.36"></line>
                <line x1="18.36" y1="5.64" x2="19.78" y2="4.22"></line>
              </svg>
              <svg class="icon-moon" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M21 12.79A9 9 0 1 1 11.21 3 7 7 0 0 0 21 12.79z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </button>

          <div class="tl-userbox glass-panel hyper-glass">
            <div class="tl-userbox__avatar">
              <span id="userInitials">7L</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tl-userbox__info">
              <div class="tl-userbox__name" id="nomeUsuario">Carregando...</div>
              <div class="tl-userbox__meta mono-font" id="metaUsuario">Conectando...</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>

      <section class="tl-ops-access-overview anim-stagger-2">
        <article class="tl-ops-access-strip">
          <div class="tl-ops-access-strip__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M4 7h16"></path>
              <path d="M4 12h16"></path>
              <path d="M4 17h16"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="tl-ops-access-strip__copy">
            <span class="mono-font">MODULO ATIVO</span>
            <strong id="opsSummaryPrimary">Carregando estrutura comercial...</strong>
            <small id="opsSummarySecondary">Unificando jornada comercial e cadastro de imoveis em um unico lugar.</small>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="tl-ops-access-strip">
          <div class="tl-ops-access-strip__icon tl-ops-access-strip__icon--secondary" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"></circle>
              <path d="M12 7v5l3 3"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="tl-ops-access-strip__copy">
            <span class="mono-font">ULTIMA VALIDACAO</span>
            <strong id="opsLastAccess">Agora ha pouco</strong>
            <small id="opsLastAccessMeta">Aba comercial pronta para crescer com novas entregas.</small>
          </div>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="tl-ops-access-metrics anim-stagger-2">
        <article class="tl-ops-access-metric">
          <span class="mono-font">ABAS</span>
          <strong id="opsKpiClientes">--</strong>
        </article>
        <article class="tl-ops-access-metric">
          <span class="mono-font">ATIVA</span>
          <strong id="opsKpiDashboards">--</strong>
        </article>
        <article class="tl-ops-access-metric">
          <span class="mono-font">EXPANSAO</span>
          <strong id="opsKpiScenes">--</strong>
        </article>
        <article class="tl-ops-access-metric">
          <span class="mono-font">STATUS</span>
          <strong id="opsKpiEscopo">--</strong>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="tl-ops-catalog-shell anim-stagger-3">
        <div class="tl-ops-catalog-shell__head">
          <div>
            <div class="tl-ops-section-kicker mono-font">ABAS DO MODULO</div>
            <h2>Clientes, Simulador e Imoveis organizados no fluxo comercial.</h2>
          </div>
          <p>
            A ordem prioriza o cliente, segue para a simulacao e termina na base de imoveis.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="tl-ops-toolbar__tabs" role="tablist" aria-label="Abas do Connect Comercial">
          <a class="tl-ops-tab is-active" href="/comercial/clientes" aria-current="page">
            <span class="tl-ops-tab__label">Clientes</span>
          </a>
          <a class="tl-ops-tab" href="/comercial/simulador">
            <span class="tl-ops-tab__label">Simulador</span>
          </a>
          <a class="tl-ops-tab" href="/comercial/imoveis">
            <span class="tl-ops-tab__label">Imoveis</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="tl-ops-catalog-shell anim-stagger-3">
        <div class="tl-ops-catalog-shell__head">
          <div>
            <div class="tl-ops-section-kicker mono-font">ABA ATIVA</div>
            <h2>Operacao comercial organizada em uma estrutura unica.</h2>
          </div>
          <p id="opsCatalogIntro">
            Abaixo esta a aba que fica ativa agora dentro do Connect Comercial.
          </p>
        </div>

        <section class="tl-ops-access-grid" id="operacoesCatalogo">
          <article class="tl-ops-empty-state">
            <span class="tl-ops-empty-state__badge mono-font">7LM</span>
            <h3>Preparando a visao comercial</h3>
            <p>Estamos carregando a configuracao do modulo.</p>
          </article>
        </section>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>

  <script src="/02_recursos/02_scripts/operacoes_shared.js?v=20260407-theme-persist1"></script>
  <script src="/02_recursos/02_scripts/operacoes_catalogo.js?v=20260407-comercial-tabs1"></script>
</body>
</html>


